description.nl:
UV Protection Swimsuit Shark
- swim suit with sharks
- UV protection 50 to EN 13758-1 (Hohenstein Institute test no. 15.1.10.0286)
- Long, padded zipper with chin guard
- fast drying material
- Oeko-Tex Standard 100 class 1, test number 11.0.86164, Hohenstein

Colour: Blue
Size: 110/116
